title: Giannis Leads the Bucks to a 2-1 Series Lead | Weekends With Wos
description:
Wos is joined by The Athletic’s Seth Partnow to discuss what the Bucks have done well in slowing down the Celtics offense, what the Celtics can do to try to even up the series, and more.

Host: Wosny Lambre
Guest: Seth Partnow
